ra City)]][[Category:11]][[sn:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:11]][[sn:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:11]] [[Category:11]][[sn:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:11]] [[Category:New]] [[Category:11]][[sn:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:11]] [[Category:11]][[en:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:11]] [[Category:qq]][[sn:Nenbutsuji Temple (Nara City)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:New]]

